A well known Nigerian politician and former Senior Special Adviser to the governor of Edo State on News Media, Jack Obinyan, has taken to his official Facebook page to react after a lady identified as Jewel Ifunaya Chika dragged the former governor of Lagos State, Bola Ahmed Adekunle Tinubu over his statement in which in claimed that without him, the President, Muhammadu Buhari would not have won the 2015 Presidential election.
It was reported that the national leader of the ruling All Progressive Congress, APC, Bola Tinubu while addressing the APD delegates claimed that without him President Muhammadu Buhari would not be won the 2015 Presidential election, adding that the President was ready to give up his ambition after he lost his first election until he gave him hope.
Reacting to this statement, Jewel Ifunaya Chika took to her Facebook page to drag Tinubu, saying that she is so pissed, adding that Bola Tinubu can attack the governor, vice president, and others, but throwing shades on the President is like throwing shades on her.
Further speaking, Ifunaya Chika stated that she followed Buhari to APC, and she’s loyal to Buhari. Ifunaya Chika asked Bola Tinubu how was he able to make Buhari the President?.
Ifunaya Chika, however, said Bola Tinubu was able to make Buhari the President, but yet he could not make Ribadu or Atiku Abubakar the President.
